{"tid":218154,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風追擊】1701號熱帶氣旋 梅花 MUIFA（03W)","createTime":"2017-04-26T10:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T07:42:46.000Z","uid":38255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58ecf8f773e0eca62fc1085220e11fc078ef2136","tid":218154,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:01:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\"><img src=\"http://x.co/wk013\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk013&h=891579e3&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>颱風追擊：熱帶氣旋梅花</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1701號熱帶氣旋 梅花 MUIFA(03W)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">來源：澳門<br />\n意義：梅花耐寒，代表中國人的堅毅。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【註】 發出颱風追擊帖，表示有熱帶氣旋在南海或西北太平洋一帶形成。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要張貼未經證實的風暴消息、使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新，直至熱帶氣旋消散。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤熱帶氣旋路徑圖</ins></span></span> <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1705.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fnwp_1705.png&h=e71fdd21&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_1705.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Ftc_1705.png&h=e32a97e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 香港天文台 (HKO)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zooml/1701-00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jma.go.jp%2Fjp%2Ftyph%2Fimages%2Fzooml%2F1701-00.png&h=8d471dfb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.jma.go.jp/jp/typh/images/zoom5l/1701-00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jma.go.jp%2Fjp%2Ftyph%2Fimages%2Fzoom5l%2F1701-00.png&h=f6bd438b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 日本氣象廳 (JMA)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://metoc.ndbc.noaa.gov/ProductFeeds-portlet/img/jtwc/products/wp0317.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetoc.ndbc.noaa.gov%2FProductFeeds-portlet%2Fimg%2Fjtwc%2Fproducts%2Fwp0317.gif&h=bb6f2932&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://www.tropicalstormrisk.com/tracker/dynamic/images/201703W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tropicalstormrisk.com%2Ftracker%2Fdynamic%2Fimages%2F201703W.png&h=552508a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 聯合颱風警報中心 (JTWC)<br />\n<img src=\"http://icons.wunderground.com/data/images/wp201703_model.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ficons.wunderground.com%2Fdata%2Fimages%2Fwp201703_model.gif&h=3329a90e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://icons-ak.wunderground.com/data/images/wp201703_ensmodel.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ficons-ak.wunderground.com%2Fdata%2Fimages%2Fwp201703_ensmodel.gif&h=0f8adc3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 全球預報系統 (GFS)<br />\n<img src=\"http://typhoon2000.ph/multi/data/MUIFA.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftyphoon2000.ph%2Fmulti%2Fdata%2FMUIFA.PNG&h=1f22ddbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 各機構綜合預測<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://tropic.ssec.wisc.edu/real-time/mimic-tc/2017_03W/webManager/last48hrs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftropic.ssec.wisc.edu%2Freal-time%2Fmimic-tc%2F2017_03W%2FwebManager%2Flast48hrs.gif&h=e2d18d4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 過去48小時動畫</strong>"},{"pid":"7632dad2185d2253060a92a3df5d2bbf2b1b1ef4","tid":218154,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"Thanks!"},{"pid":"e357b60d18d307d1330c7f7561ce5de90d969a62","tid":218154,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T10:07:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><ins>◤颱風追擊必備資訊</ins></span></span><br />