ttps://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fegsicyzd&h=7181f14e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">氣象台專頁正式登場</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>我們自2008年起發表氣象帖。現在，一個屬於巴打絲打們的天氣專頁正式登場！我們以淺白易明的方式介紹氣象，讓您享受認識氣象箇中的樂趣。氣象不再沉悶空泛。<br />\n本專頁旨在為大家提供氣象相關的資訊，其中包括一些氣象小資料、即時的天氣及風暴等消息。設立的主要目的，是為了讓比較忙碌的巴打絲打們，即使沒時間或沒留意到高登氣象帖，都可透過另一個渠道獲得我們的氣象資訊。<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">請巴打絲打們到專頁讚好以示對我們支持及鼓勵</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=c092dbb2\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=d4a0212b\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/UTube\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FUTube&h=a22db7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=7b5121bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a></em></strong>"},{"pid":"7d19918963feea3cc54fc504a3de597b3ec298ca","tid":218154,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"綠荼留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53895091acf6e6161f4c08a6e4562d86f1b43770","tid":218154,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,